{"tid":604483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣ptt網友　聞香港租金　驚奇：租金貴過人工？不可能","createTime":"2018-03-24T17:18:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T11:11:25.000Z","uid":47714,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"207d477348b81f8c385ad5406acccff54a8a1a7a","tid":604483,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T17:18:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.ptt.cc/bbs/historia/M.1336286580.A.444.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2Fhistoria%2FM.1336286580.A.444.html&d=pTH8vu00OQ1UBhlUUSJVLJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=388d84ad\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ptt.cc/bbs/historia/M.1336286580.A.444.html</a><br />\n<br />\n 作者　chenglap (無想流流星拳)　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　 看板　historia<br />\n 時間　Sun May　6 14:42:58 2012<br />\n───────────────────────────────────────<br />\n<br />\n&rarr; innominate:這我不清楚,但租金漲過薪資的話,除非去搶銀行否則怎租?<br />\n&rarr; innominate:而一般的上班族薪資就那樣,你漲租金只是讓你房子沒錢收<br />\n&rarr; zeuklie:所以可見台北房價高薪資低 逼房東要降租金配合薪資水準<br />\n&rarr; chenglap:香港就是寧可把屋空著也不會廉租給你.<br />\n&rarr; chenglap:簡單來說, 一個單位 300% 不降價, 好過三個單位 100%.<br />\n&rarr; innominate:香港這樣的情形很妙,也許有空再來研究一下<br />\n&rarr; innominate:理論上能賺一天是一天,因為你不廉租別人也會廉租<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ptt.cc/bbs/historia/M.1336482130.A.ED1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2Fhistoria%2FM.1336482130.A.ED1.html&d=pTH8vu00OQ1UBhlUUSJVLJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=51e2ea54\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ptt.cc/bbs/historia/M.1336482130.A.ED1.html</a><br />\n<br />\n 作者　dashanew (dasha)　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　看板　historia<br />\n 時間　Tue May　8 21:02:07 2012<br />\n───────────────────────────────────────<br />\n<br />\n推 obov:台北的房租/房價比　拿出去看真的是房租超便宜<br />\n&rarr; zeuklie:精確點來說是房租又比店租便宜非常多<br />\n推 Morisato:台北房子出租20年可能還沒回收一半,房租便宜到爆...<br />\n&rarr; kanako:台北市我有聽過房屋售價可以租同一間房子一百年的<br />\n&rarr; innominate:大台北地區的空房率很高,你不想租出去但別人想<br />\n推 bobju:呵呵,總有房市崩盤的一天,到時就會平衡租金比例. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73fe18c085c017d26f7b33b36a88becd4d26ab7e","tid":604483,"uid":47714,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T17:19:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1390368304.A.053.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1390368304.A.053.html&d=pTH8vu00OQ1UBhlUUSJVLJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=2b2150fa\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1390368304.A.053.html</a><br />\n<br />\n 作者　chenglap (無想流流星拳)　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　看板　Gossiping<br />\n 標題　Re: [新聞] 逆天！香港房價所得比14.9倍<br />\n 時間　Wed Jan 22 13:25:01 2014<br />\n───────────────────────────────────────<br />\n<br />\n1. 年輕人當然是買不起房, 別說普通的年輕人, 連當一些高薪職業的專業人士<br />\n　 也抱怨買不起, 月入四萬港幣以上的醫生和律師都覺得負擔很重. 因為他們<br />\n　 月入四五萬, 可是房貸要還的可能就薪水一半, 還有他們要交稅.<br />\n<br />\n2. 至於推文說「買不起就租啊」, 在香港也是不太可行的, 因為香港和臺北不<br />\n　 同的地方是租金也很貴, 租值比率約算是臺北的四倍, 換句話說, 同樣價錢<br />\n　 的樓, 香港的租金是臺北四倍, 買不起的人, 靠租也是半條人命了.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ps.hket.com/article/902930/%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E5%A4%9A%E5%B9%B4%E7%9A%84%E3%80%8C%E4%BE%9B%E5%B9%B3%E9%81%8E%E7%A7%9F%E3%80%8D%E5%AE%9A%E5%BE%8B%E5%B0%87%E3%80%8C%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%8C%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F902930%2F%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%25BA%258C%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%259A%2584%25E3%2580%258C%25E4%25BE%259B%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E9%2581%258E%25E7%25A7%259F%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B0%2587%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%258E%25A9%25E5%25AE%258C%25E3%2580%258D%25EF%25BC%259F&d=pTH8vu00OQ1UBhlUUSJVLJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=7878445b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ps.hket.com/article/902930/%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E5%A4%9A%E5%B9%B4%E7%9A%84%E3%80%8C%E4%BE%9B%E5%B9%B3%E9%81%8E%E7%A7%9F%E3%80%8D%E5%AE%9A%E5%BE%8B%E5%B0%87%E3%80%8C%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%8C%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%9F</a><br />\n<br />\n2015年10月21日 7:55<br />\n<br />\n持續已有7至8年的「供平過租」定律<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1473658980419&amp;issue=20160912\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantp2.php%3Fnode%3D1473658980419%26issue%3D20160912&d=pTH8vu00OQ1UBhlUUSJVLJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=7b8a9aa7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1473658980419&amp;issue=20160912</a><br />\n<br />\n中原陳永傑：供平過租至少持續兩年<br />\n<br />\n文章日期：2016年9月12日 13:41<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10152248080852357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10152248080852357&d=pTH8vu00OQ1UBhlUUSJVLJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=0de3ec73\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10152248080852357</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：chenglap<br />\n<br />\n香港要增強競爭力, 所有物業減租 75% 就可以做到了, 不需要放棄母語. 你放棄了母語, 你的租還是比別人貴四倍. 我看不出競爭力在哪.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nForest Chui: 即係放棄高地價政策。<br />\n<br />\nCheng Lap: 連幾十年的舊樓都可以收成萬銀租, 不是因為高地價政策"},{"pid":"d684a4aec1bbd6e20ec9600512e5ed315fc23fca","tid":604483,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T03:00:10.000Z","msg":"減租同意"},{"pid":"51c594af258896e24bbf709bee8510c5fea963b9","tid":604483,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T03:01:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f3e52bc33517172964e3e714f4f07db08ac05ad","tid":604483,"uid":20241,"like":10,"dislike":15,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T03:11:40.000Z","msg":"on9<br />\n我地呢啲業主咁辛苦買層樓<br />\n點解要平租俾啲賤民？<br />\n大把人租得起"},{"pid":"27323b1372a423cd8c3b93247e4bccabc87a4ea0","tid":604483,"uid":76098,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2f3e52bc33517172964e3e714f4f07db08ac05ad","tid":604483,"uid":20241,"like":10,"dislike":15,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T03:11:40.000Z","msg":"on9<br />\n我地呢啲業主咁辛苦買層樓<br />\n點解要平租俾啲賤民？<br />\n大把人租得起"},"citedBy":1,"replyTim